AI Annotation Workflows

A repository that models structured AI annotation and human feedback workflows used in modern machine learning and LLM training systems.


Overview

This project demonstrates how annotation pipelines are designed to improve AI model quality through structured labeling and evaluation processes.


Objectives

- Simulate annotation workflows
- Create labeling guidelines
- Improve annotation consistency
- Design QA systems for AI training data
- Study evaluator agreement


